headline.main: A Taste of Spain as Bayern Ease Past Cologne
headline.print_headline: A Taste of Spain as Bayern Ease Past Cologne

lead_paragraph: Spaniards Javi Martinez and Juan Bernat scored their first league goals of the season to give Bayern Munich a comfortable 3-0 victory at Cologne on Saturday and move seven points clear at the top of the Bundesliga.
